$ /usr/share/alsa/alsa.conf
-

`/usr/share/alsa/alsa.conf` is the main entry point fo rconfiguring the ALSA system. It usually calls (sources?)
→ Linux/fhs/home/username/_asoundrc.

Apparently, → Linux/fhs/etc/asound_conf is an alternative location for `/usr/share/alsa/alsa.conf`.

sa:
  → Linux/sound/ALSA
